'''AutoHotkey'''是[[自由软件|自由]][[开源软件|开源]]的編程語言，常用於Windows平台的自動化。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://cedeq.com/blog/automation/prevent-rsi-with-autohotkey/ | title=Prevent RSI with AutoHotkey | publisher=cedeq.com | accessdate=2014-03-02 | archive-date=2014-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302062318/http://cedeq.com/blog/automation/prevent-rsi-with-autohotkey/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== AutoHotkey 能快速編寫的功能 ==
*启动程序，打開文件
* 獲得或產生系統狀態，音量（狀態，調節），搜索螢幕上的图像或像素（獲得坐標），鼠標（位置，懸停視窗對象，移動），鍵盤（[[热键|热键]]（快捷鍵），热字串（鍵盤輸入序列），上下文热键），[[游戏杆|游戏杆]]按鈕
* 创建[[图形用户界面|图形用户界面]]
* 剪貼簿操作，程序窗口操作



==历史==
AutoHotkey Basic时期，官方网站为[http://www.autohotkey.com www.autohotkey.com]{{Wayback|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/ |date=20110621062330 }}。当Chris Mallett（原作者）停止更新时宣布AutoHotkey_L为后续主分支。<ref>{{cite web|author=Chris|title=My status and website changes|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/board/topic/58864-my-status-and-website-changes/|publisher=AutoHotkey.com|accessdate=2014-06-15|archive-date=2014-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009103946/http://www.autohotkey.com/board/topic/58864-my-status-and-website-changes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不久网站转由polyethene管理，他对网站的决定与论坛中许多核心用户出现较大分歧<ref>{{cite web|author=polyethene|title=Changes for AutoHotkey website|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/board/topic/79177-changes/|publisher=AutoHotkey.com|accessdate=2014-06-15|archive-date=2014-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009103948/http://www.autohotkey.com/board/topic/79177-changes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=sumon|title=Make AHK_L "main" version?|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/board/topic/77316-make-ahk-l-main-version/|publisher=AutoHotkey.com|accessdate=2014-06-15|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714215625/http://www.autohotkey.com/board/topic/77316-make-ahk-l-main-version/|dead-url=no}}</ref>且不时失去联系并成立了公司确保其正常运营。<ref>{{cite web|title=Basics as to why AHKSCRIPT exists|url=http://ahkscript.org/boards/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=466|accessdate=2014-06-15|author=tidbit|publisher=ahkscript.com|archive-date=2014-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727200837/http://ahkscript.org/boards/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=466|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The AutoHotkey Foundation|url=http://ahkscript.org/foundation/|publisher=ahkscript.org|accessdate=2014-06-15|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625200732/http://ahkscript.org/foundation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Welcome and if you need help|url=http://ahkscript.org/boards/viewtopic.php?f=3&t=7|accessdate=2014-06-15|author=tank|publisher=ahkscript.org|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714225800/http://ahkscript.org/boards/viewtopic.php?f=3&t=7|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年4月成立了 AutoHotkey Foundation 以確保AutoHotkey自由开放、持续开发，並提供组织、法务和财政上的支持。<ref>{{cite web|title=The AutoHotkey Foundation|url=http://ahkscript.org/foundation/|accessdate=2014-06-29|publisher=ahkscript.org|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625200732/http://ahkscript.org/foundation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

