== 版本歷史 ==

* AutoHotkey Basic：Chris Mallett 提议在[[AutoIt|AutoIt]] v2中集成[[热键|热键]]支持未得到AutoIt社区响应后，于2003年11月10日公开发布了AutoHotkey的首个[[軟件出版週期|测试]]版本。<ref>{{cite web|title=Author Chris Mallett's post on the AutoHotkey Forums|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=20176#20176|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Autohotkey.com|archive-date=2008-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080218024503/http://www.autohotkey.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=20176#20176|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=An AutoIt / AutoHotkey nonfunctional comparison|url=http://paperlined.org/apps/autohotkey/autoit_and_autohotkey.html|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Paperlined.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208181846/http://paperlined.org/apps/autohotkey/autoit_and_autohotkey.html|archive-date=2011-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AutoHotkey Changelog for Years 2003-2004|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/changelog/2004.htm|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Autohotkey.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104142142/http://www.autohotkey.com/changelog/2004.htm|archivedate=2011-11-04|deadurl=yes}}</ref>作者以AutoIt v2的语法为基础并在一些命令和编译器中使用AutoIt v3的源码开始编写自己的程序。<ref>{{cite web|title=Author Chris Mallett's post on the AutoHotkey Forums|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=19710#19710|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Autohotkey.com|archive-date=2008-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080526001248/http://www.autohotkey.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=19710#19710|dead-url=yes}}</ref>随后，AutoIt v3的许可从[[GPL|GPL]]切换为[[专有软件|闭源]]，作者给出的原因是“某些项目重复窃取AutoIt的代码”和“建立了竞争者”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Licensing Opinions - AutoIt Forums|url=http://www.autoitscript.com/forum/index.php?showtopic=7204|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Autoitscript.com|archive-date=2019-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919053313/https://www.autoitscript.com/forum/topic/7204-licensing-opinions/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* AutoHotkey_L：2010年10月10日，原作者在停止更新一年多后表示“失去了兴趣”并声明AutoHotkey_L为正在开发的分支，并把它放置在网页的下载部分的前面。<ref>{{cite web|title=Forum post by Chris, announcing AutoHotkey_L now main platform|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63474|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Autohotkey.com|archive-date=2019-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919053312/https://autohotkey.com/board/topic/58864-my-status-and-website-changes/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同时把原来的版本称为 AutoHotkey Basic。<ref>{{cite web|title=Download page showing AutoHotkey_L as ongoing platform|url=http://www.autohotkey.com/download/|accessdate=2011-12-02|date=|publisher=Autohotkey.com|archive-date=2011-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111201221255/http://www.autohotkey.com/download/|dead-url=no}}</ref>比起AutoHotkey Basic，AutoHotkey_L中增加了[[Unicode|Unicode]]、[[组件对象模型|COM]]、[[对象_(计算机科学)|对象]]、[[调试|调试]]特性和其他功能。<ref name="AHKL_Features" />

